snippet.title: Gord - 16 Minutes of Gameplay | gamescom 2022
snippet.description:
Here’s an extended look at some new Gord gameplay for the upcoming dark fantasy strategy adventure game from Covenant dev and Team17. Get a feel for the game’s systems and see how you’ll go about managing a settlement and its inhabitants in this world-first look at its pre-beta build. Gord is coming soon to PC.

#IGN #Gord
